  "rows": [
    {
      "id": "video-promo-public",
      "title": "Welcome to The Looth Group",
      "type": "video-promo",
      "layout": "video-promo",
      "column": "main",
      "audience": "public",
      "query": {
        "side": "video-right",
        "video_id": "2IBxue3zPxE",
        "aspect": "16x9",
        "html": "<p class=\"vp-eyebrow\">Welcome</p><h3>Built by guitar looths, for guitar looths.</h3><p>The Looth Group is where serious luthiers and builders share tools, techniques, and the candid conversations you cannot find on YouTube. It is a working community — not a marketing channel.</p><ul><li>The full archive of build threads, repair tutorials, and shop-tested fixes.</li><li>Member video library — long-form workshops from working looths.</li><li>Downloads: plans, jigs, templates, and reference files.</li><li>Active discussion forum where questions actually get answered.</li></ul><p><a class=\"vp-cta\" href=\"https://www.patreon.com/c/theloothgroup/membership\">Join Looth Group →</a><a class=\"vp-cta vp-cta--secondary\" href=\"https://loothgroup.com/looth-group-weekly/\">Weekly email</a></p>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "video-promo-members",
      "title": "What's new",
      "type": "video-promo",
      "layout": "video-promo",
      "column": "main",
      "audience": "members",
      "query": {
        "side": "video-right",
        "video_id": "LhcIQ0x31hc",
        "aspect": "16x9",
        "html": "<p class=\"vp-eyebrow\">What's new</p><h3>Welcome to the new Looth Group website</h3><p>We rebuilt the whole site around one idea: everything the group makes &mdash; discussions, videos, articles, plans &mdash; in one place, and fast. The quick tour:</p><ul><li><strong>The Hub</strong> &mdash; every discussion and new piece of content in one feed. Tap <strong>Filters</strong> to narrow by category or type, and the bookmark on any card saves it to your <strong>Saved</strong> list.</li><li><strong>Your profile</strong> &mdash; your shop's page: skills, gallery, credentials, location. Edit it from your avatar menu; use the arrows (or drag) to reorder sections, and the privacy slider decides who sees what.</li><li><strong>The Map &amp; Directory</strong> &mdash; find looths near you. What shows on the map is up to each member's own privacy setting.</li><li><strong>Events &amp; Loothalong</strong> &mdash; workshops and live streams on one calendar; the green banner means we're live now.</li><li><strong>Messages</strong> &mdash; DM any member straight from their profile.</li><li><strong>Make it an app</strong> &mdash; on your phone, open the site and choose <em>Add to Home Screen</em>. Full app feel, no app store.</li></ul><hr class=\"vp-divider\"><p>It's all live and still moving &mdash; your feedback decides what we build next. Something off, broken, or missing? Tell us.</p><p><a class=\"vp-cta\" data-feedback href=\"/hub/?compose=suggestion-box-bug-reporting\">Report a bug or suggestion &rarr;</a><a class=\"vp-cta vp-cta--secondary\" href=\"/hub/?compose\">Start a thread</a></p>"
      }
    },
